						               													<description>Katana Schoolgirls vs Zombie Furries is a tabletop minigame for 1-4 players. Players take the role of a katana-wielding schoolgirl, battling the forces of darkness and sometimes&amp;#10;each other.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To play you will need a cardstock figure or traditional miniature for each figure in the game, two or more six-sided dice, a playset (sample tiles included in the game), Character Cards, an Event Deck, Talent Cards, Dark Secret Cards and lots and lots of zombie miniatures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The objective of the game is to hunt down and destroy the zombies and collect gear. Each opponent and gear has a point cost that is added at the end of the game to determine the winner. Objectives can shift during the game depending on the game scenario you are playing and your character&amp;rsquo;s Dark Secret motivation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Nominated for the 2012 Ennies Best Miniature Product Award&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
